{"tid":1814330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我地「卍夢●遺卍」 正式宣布退出運動。","createTime":"2020-01-07T01:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T09:08:44.000Z","uid":216555,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63b2b89630bee00b3a0ac4eac9bf7067468e8c44","tid":1814330,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:09:35.000Z","msg":"運動初期 我等行動都會有人借AV或用手幫我地善後<br />\n以致我地全數人可以功成身退 擇日再戰。<br />\n去到11月頭八名成員虛脫過度 其中兩名至今昏迷不醒<br />\n對我地卍夢●遺卍打擊甚重，當中不乏夢遺大師及手天使<br />\n經過最近屌鬼事件越多，嚴重影響卍夢●遺卍將來行動<br />\n所以在此宣布餘下成員將退出抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n今日起我地會著重物色及培訓新女優 以維持小隊雄風<br />\n但日後屌鬼依然嚴重 我地會戒丁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n由於有兩名成員虛脫 我地經討論後視為死亡<br />\n所以我地拆開咗紙巾黎睇<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一個寫光複香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n屌你寫錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日笑你文盲 點知你真係文盲<br />\n不過好多謝你地兩個 <br />\n你兩個孖寶兄弟帶咗好多歡樂比我地 係我地既開心果<br />\n我地唔會忘記你地。<br />\n<br />\n夢遺●大師 絕筆"},{"pid":"d7bfe295f0050cad5aaeb070f5bd6e0544f753ef","tid":1814330,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PAFz6D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PAFz6D.gif&h=fbf2cad5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ae8885c67161ebe655fb683cc344927c06ac2ad","tid":1814330,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.complex.com/complex/images/c_fill,g_center,h_640,w_640/fl_lossy,pg_1,q_auto/he0es3dbhdzkss2elek7/pompeii-pleasure-seeker\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.complex.com%2Fcomplex%2Fimages%2Fc_fill%2Cg_center%2Ch_640%2Cw_640%2Ffl_lossy%2Cpg_1%2Cq_auto%2Fhe0es3dbhdzkss2elek7%2Fpompeii-pleasure-seeker&h=09a63ce3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"448afed94eca3b202b4cde02526cf2a97a00a753","tid":1814330,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:16:40.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\n死5毛乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/n